OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK cities told they must   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprepare for wildfires      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Last week's wildfires across London    
OL,6, show that lessons learned tackling     
OL,7, rural blazes must urgently be applied  
OL,8, to built-up areas, fire chiefs say.    
OL,10,FThe record-breaking heatwave, with 40C 
OL,11,Fpeaks, came during a prolonged spell of
OL,12,Fdry weather - and that dried out       
OL,13,Fgardens, verges and green spaces.      
OL,15,FThat helped to spark the kind of blazes
OL,16,Fmore commonly seen in the countryside. 
OL,18,FMore than 40 houses and shops were     
OL,19,Fdestroyed after a number of grass fires
OL,20,Fspread to nearby buildings.            
